overview:
JT TechnoSoft is a business consulting and marketing solutions company based in Canada.

Innovation is our motivation. Initially started as a technology solutions provider JT TechnoSoft Inc. is now concentrating on how its customers can be benefited from the rapidly changing Information Technology and its influence on business innovation and development.

Be that a small business promotion platform, major product/brand recognition, child-friendly social networking platform, or an employment resource, JT TechnoSoft has the right team to find right business solution with an excellent business value.

Customer trust is our business investment. We always thrive to provide customer-first quality-best business solutions either custom-tailored or for wider business audience. While we invest in new innovative business ideas, our current projects are innovative, consumer-centric and cost-efficient business solutions.
